It was another great week: Matt Belloni and Kim Masters scrutinized Iger=E2=
=80=99s $16 million Trump payoff while Eriq Gardner identified the town=E2=
=80=99s new D.O.J. headache; Dylan Byers got into the Stephanopoulos of it =
all; Lauren Sherman previewed Versace=E2=80=99s next home; Rachel Strugatz =
spoke with Gwyneth
Paltrow=E2=80=99s Goop whisperer; Bill Cohan examined David Zaslav=E2=80=99=
s various cable options; John Ourand conveyed ESPN=E2=80=99s simmering NBA =
anxieties; Marion Maneker dug up the roots on the $32 million Judy Garland =
ruby slipper sale; and Baratunde Thurston articulated Wall Street=E2=80=99s=
 views on A.I. Meanwhile, Tara Palmeri offered a talmudic reading of Trump=
